data.description: All New Carpets and Main Level just painted.   Granite counters * Updated Kitchen & Bathrooms. Features Include: 4 Bedrooms * BRIGHT  KITCHEN & Bathrooms * Deck * Pool * You want PRIVACY - but still be part of a FANTASTIC NEIGHBORHOOD - Here you have a Private Yard and Setting * and a GREAT neighborhood location!!  Finished Lower Level with Newer Pellet Stove 2017 *  4th BR in Lower Level, Plus additional room that can be an office or storage!  * Short drive to the Chesapeake Bay!!
